      "body": "[temporary] T14 (run 0015 session 0014-horizon-T14): fibre-connector layer landed, full build green (8666 jobs, exit 0).\n\nAdded to Picard/SerreFiniteness.lean (still exactly ONE sorry = the leaf sectionGradedModule_fg):\n- Scheme.Hom.IsProjectiveWith.fiber \u2014 AXIOM-CLEAN. IsProjectiveWith descends to the scheme-theoretic fibre X_s = pi.fiber s; literally h.baseChange (S.fromSpecResidueField s) since Mathlib's fiber IS the base change (fiber = pullback pi (fromSpecResidueField s), fiberToSpecResidueField = pullback.snd).\n- Scheme.Hom.fiberModule_isFinitePresentation \u2014 AXIOM-CLEAN via the sorry-free Modules.pullback_isFinitePresentation.\n- sectionGradedModule_fg_fiber \u2014 conclusions 1+2 (ring Noetherian, module finite) of the leaf at the fibre; sorryAx-only.\n- hilbertFunction_finiteDimensional \u2014 conclusion 3 (each Gamma(X_s, F_s\u2297L_s^m) finite-dim/\u03ba(s)), stated with hilbertFunction's fiberSectionsModule structure; sorryAx-only. = the FINITENESS HALF of the I-0109 Hilbert-lane bridge.\n\nBlueprint Picard_QuotScheme.tex: 4 new nodes after lem:projective_with_base_change (lem:projective_with_fiber, lem:fiberModule_finitePresentation both fully \\leanok; lem:sectionGradedModule_fg_fiber, lem:hilbertFunction_finiteDimensional statement-\\leanok only).\n\nREMAINING I-0109 bridge (item 2) still open, precise shape: gradedModule_hilbertSeries_rational (GradedHilbertSerre.lean:1243) needs M=\u2295\u0393(X_s,F_s\u2297L_s^m) finite over MvPolynomial(Fin r) \u03ba(s) via r=d+1 DEGREE-1 coordinate endos. Leaf conclusion 2 only gives 'finite over the abstract section graded ring R(X_s,L_s)' \u2014 a FORM MISMATCH. Reaching the engine input needs R(X_s,L_s) finite over \u03ba[coordinates] (coordinate sections i^*x_j \u2208 \u0393(X_s,L_s) + their endos + MvPoly-finiteness), interlocked with computing \u0393(\u2119^d,O(1)) (unbuilt). RECOMMENDATION: when the leaf is eventually proved, restate its conclusion 2 (or add a companion) directly as the MvPolynomial(Fin d+1)-finiteness engine-input tuple so the engine call becomes sorry-free glue. Details in memory serre-finiteness-leaf-decomposition.",
